      { "@type": "Question", "name": "What is the shortest word with J in Scrabble?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "JO is the shortest J word at just 2 letters, scoring 9 points. It means a Scottish term of endearment and is valid in both SOWPODS and TWL dictionaries." }},
