        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-amber-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">⚠️ Dictionary Check</p>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-200">Always verify your dictionary before a game. In tournament play, SOWPODS-only words played in a TWL game will be <span class="text-white font-medium">challenged off the board</span> and you lose your turn. Use our Word Finder's dictionary toggle to check validity.</p>
